            "title": "美台達成降低關稅協議 還涉及5000億美元晶片投資和授信",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美台達成降低關稅協議 還涉及5000億美元晶片投資和授信\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cAfDRUHmrRfHAkMb3kz9MQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/931e03e0-f262-11f0-97f7-ccaf512dd735\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美台達成降低關稅協議 還涉及5000億美元晶片投資和授信</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
